Using Creat React app::

npm config set cache "C:\Users\Firstname~1\AppData\Roaming\npm-cache" --global

npx create-react-app my-app
cd my-app
npm start

npm run build-----> creates the html css which the browser will read while deployment(converted).

BABEL:: Take all the javscript files and make sure they run in all browsers not matter how old they are.

WEBPACK:: Modular bundler, 

build folder will be used for deployment,
src folder is our playground.